## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-312">`WriteEvent`方法提供多載的字串與整數引數的組合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-312">The `WriteEvent` method provides overloads with combinations of string and integer arguments.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-313">如果沒有這些組合的符合呼叫參數時，編譯器會使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>多載，也就是比其他多載慢很多。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-313">If none of these combinations match the parameters for the call, the compiler uses the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> overload, which is considerably slower than the other overloads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-314">請參閱詳細資料的多載頁面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-314">See the overload page for details.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-315">在所有情況下，`eventid`參數必須大於 0 或小於 65535 或在作業中，可能會發生錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-315">In all cases, the `eventid` parameter should be greater than 0 or less than 65535 or errors can occur in the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-316">如果發生錯誤，您可以取得有關錯誤的來源的詳細資訊檢查輸出資料流的偵錯工具，如果您有偵錯工具附加至處理程序引發的事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-316">If errors do occur, you can get more information about the source of the error by checking the output stream of the debugger, if you have a debugger attached to the process firing events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-317">如果有發生錯誤的事件來源的 ETW 接聽程式，您也可以尋找的 ETW 事件資料流中報告的錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-317">You can also look for errors reported in the ETW event stream, if you have an ETW listener on the event source where the error occurs.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-318">當您實作識別為中的 ETW 事件方法<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-衍生的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-318">When you implement a method that is identified as an ETW event in an <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-derived class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-319">您必須先呼叫基底類別<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>方法傳遞<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A>和實作的方法類似於下列範例相同的引數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-319">You must call the base class <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> method passing the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A> and the same arguments as the implemented method similar to the following example.</span></span>  
  
```  
[Event(2, Level = EventLevel.Informational)]  
public void Info1(string arg1)  
{  
 base.WriteEvent(2, arg1);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-320">您也可以建立自訂的多載使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-320">You can also create a custom overload by using the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A> method.</span></span>

  
  
