## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-512">`eventid` 必須大於 0 或小於 65535 或在作業中，可能會發生錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-512">`eventid` should be greater than 0 or less than 65535 or errors can occur in the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-513">如果發生錯誤，您可以取得有關錯誤的來源的詳細資訊檢查輸出資料流的偵錯工具，如果您有偵錯工具附加至處理程序引發的事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-513">If errors do occur, you can get more information about the source of the error by checking the output stream of the debugger, if you have a debugger attached to the process firing events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-514">如果有發生錯誤的事件來源的 ETW 接聽程式，您也可以尋找的 ETW 事件資料流中報告的錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-514">You can also look for errors reported in the ETW event stream, if you have an ETW listener on the event source where the error occurs.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-515">此受保護的方法可讓使用者定義新<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>會較快，提供多載的多載。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-515">This protected method  enables users to define new <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> overloads that are faster than the provided overloads.</span></span>   <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-516">建立新的多載包含 unsafe 程式碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-516">Creating a new overload involves unsafe code.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-517">基本程序是堆疊配置事件資料的描述項的陣列，符合的內容項目數目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-517">The basic procedure is to stack-allocate an array of event data descriptors that matches the number of payload items.</span></span>   <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-518">每個內容項目，設定正確的大小，在事件值資料陣列。呼叫<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A>與初始化的陣列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-518">For each payload item, set the correct size and value in the event data array.Call <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A> with the initialized array.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-519">下列範例示範如何將加入<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>接受四個引數的多載。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-519">The following example shows how to add a <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> overload that accepts four arguments.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-520">範例就是如果您有記錄事件的記錄檔和 3 的整數的字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-520">An example would be if you have a logging event that logs a string and 3 integers.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
[Event(1)]  
public void LogTime(string tag, int hour, int minute, int second)   
{  
    WriteEvent(1, tag, hour, minute, second);  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-521">您無法執行這項操作而不需呼叫<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A>，但它必須是比速度較慢。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-521">You could do this without calling <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A>, but it would be slower than it needs to be.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-522">這是因為它會使用陣列 」 和 「 反映找出要執行的工作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-522">That is because it uses arrays and reflection to figure out what to do.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-523">如果您將記錄這些以較高的速率 (> 1000年數 / 秒)，它可以是值得進行快速的協助程式，如下列範例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-523">If you log these at a high rate (> 1000 / sec), it can be worth making a fast helper, as shown in the following example.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-524">方法會遮蔽現有<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-524">The method shadows the existing <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-525">因此原始呼叫端程式碼 (LogTime) 實際上並未變更，但 C# 編譯器會將程式將會更快更具特製化的版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-525">Thus the original caller code (LogTime) does not actually change, but the C# compiler will use the more specialized version which will be faster.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fab4-526">若要編譯 unsafe 程式碼，您必須指定[/unsafe （C# 編譯器選項）](~/docs/csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/unsafe-compiler-option.md)編譯器選項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fab4-526">To compile unsafe code, you must specify the [/unsafe (C# Compiler Options)](~/docs/csharp/language-reference/compiler-options/unsafe-compiler-option.md) compiler option.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
class AnotherEventSource : EventSource {  
  
    [NonEvent]  
    public unsafe void WriteEvent(int eventId, string arg1, int arg2, int arg3, int arg4)  
    {  
  
        fixed (char* arg1Ptr = arg1)  
        {  
            EventData* dataDesc = stackalloc EventData[4];  
  
            dataDesc[0].DataPointer = (IntPtr)arg1Ptr;  
            dataDesc[0].Size = (arg1.Length + 1) * 2; // Size in bytes, including a null terminator.   
            dataDesc[1].DataPointer = (IntPtr)(&arg2);  
            dataDesc[1].Size = 4;  
            dataDesc[2].DataPointer = (IntPtr)(&arg3);  
            dataDesc[2].Size = 4;  
            dataDesc[3].DataPointer = (IntPtr)(&arg4);  
            dataDesc[3].Size = 4;  
  
            WriteEventCore(eventId, 4, dataDesc);  
        }  
    }  
}  
  
```
